snippet.title: Anno 2205: Asteroid Miner - Launch Trailer [INT]
snippet.description:
Download for FREE now: 
App Store: *https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/anno-2205-asteroid-miner/id1013884483?l=fr&ls=1&mt=8
Google Play: *https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ubisoft.anno2205comp

From the makers of the award-winning Anno games comes a galactic Match-3 adventure with MORE THAN 180 MISSIONS for thrilling mobile action!

If you own the PC version of Anno 2205, you can transfer RARE MATERIALS from the app into the game.
